7,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"零售即刻pk"},{"pid":"3ef5195e315bff697f3a96607a2aa90435368bc8","tid":2341365,"uid":48973,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"返工先比出街<br />\n放假就唔俾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a961c69d7a230209032c15b15a4b52858bd4f057","tid":2341365,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"on9,香港都有人放閒日,紅日要返工㗎！"},{"pid":"668598be779b8005190e6e7829bb1d12c89af5c8","tid":2341365,"uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"實比人司法覆核告歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045cd3b040158d52d7708e83a3e79abf6e93352e","tid":2341365,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"bilibala呱啦呱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f0ef5c422b6834676c919590dea0c260303eff","tid":2341365,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"支持，但下個禮拜三即刻入紙立法會改599唔該"},{"pid":"07307a6d7f2663c0b399268871ce90e0b7b47c84","tid":2341365,"uid":178875,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T10:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXOOCrdP.gif&amp;h=198b8501&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"3adc2b7b4ee4ad18bbd999d8992e22249add670b","tid":2341365,"uid":362121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72fb903ae3bf0426ae032c0b7c4f6639ce4d9e9c","tid":2341365,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yim